function Sign(){
    return(

         <form>
             <label htmlFor="fullname"/>
             <input type="text" id="fullname" name="fullname">FullName</input>
 
             <label htmlFor="email"/>
             <input type="text" id="email" name="email">E-mail</input>
 
             <label htmlFor="phone"/>
             <input type="text" id="phone" name="phone">Phone No.</input>
 
             <label htmlFor="password"/>
             <input type="text" id="password" name="password">Password</input>
 
             <label htmlFor="confirmPassword"/>
             <input type="text" id="confirmPassword" name="confirmPassword">Confirm Password</input>
         </form>
    
    )
 }
 
 export default Sign;
